'''Chanlon''' was an incredibly dense{{fact}} and rare [[Ore/Legends|ore]]<ref name="KotOR2">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''</ref> that was the constituent of [[phobium]].{{fact}} It could also be combined with [[hfredium]] to form the alloy known as [[Havod/Legends|havod]].<ref name="TCSWE">{{CSWECite|II|26|havod}}</ref>

Chanlon was mined on [[Christophsis/Legends|Christophsis]].<ref name="TEA">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref>

During the [[Galactic War]], between [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] and [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|Sith Empire]], chanlon was used to build [[Armor/Legends|armors]] and weapons.<ref name="TOR">''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''</ref> Chanlon was used by [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshans]] in forging their [[Trandoshan sword|blades]], making them more effective.<ref name="KotOR2" />

